fields.description:
Setting the "verticalAlign" property with a string value on iOS does not work, while it works fine on Android is [documented|https://titaniumsdk.com/api/titanium/ui/label.html#verticalalign] as a {{Number|String}} property.

*Example*:
{code:js}
const win = Ti.UI.createWindow({
    backgroundColor: '#fff'
});

const view = Ti.UI.createView({
    backgroundColor: '#f0f0f0',
    height: 200,
    width: 200
});

view.add(Ti.UI.createLabel({
    text: 'Hello world',
    verticalAlign: 'top',
    height: Ti.UI.FILL,
    width: Ti.UI.FILL
}));

win.add(view);
win.open();
{code}
